# Assets Intangible Impairment Intangible Assets With A Finite Life Amount

## identifier
de2767

## type
float

## definition
Report the value, as at the reporting date, of accumulated amortisation and impairment on intangible assets with a finite life, as determined in accordance with relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Assets.Intangible.Impairment.IntangibleAssetsWithAFiniteLife.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo7.02.00
- period=instant
